---
title: Mediterranean Haloumi & Creamy Pesto Burger with Caramelised Onion & Kumara Wedges
description: We’re so excited about this burger, with crispy chunks of squeaky level-one haloumi, creamy pesto and a side of golden kumara wedges. Let’s just say you won’t need the local pub’s menu on hand when you’ve got this recipe under your belt.
